metadata.name: Digital Renaissance Era
metadata.description:
D.R.E. Still 
(Digital Renaissance Era) 
Artists back on top, locked up on the block
'Cause when I mint the drops I wanna rock
Best believe the pic ain't stock when I hit the spot
Real ones say good morning but paper hands keep scrollin'
How Brother? Generational wealth for all (Brother)
See a friend grinding? Go retweet it
The game done changed
Bags got fumbled but we gonna make it
(If you ain't up on thangs) 
DeFi is the name
And we're ahead of the game
Still trading Eth, 
Still got NFTs, still not loving gas fees
Still rockin' the same digital PFP
Still have my community, reppin' invisibly (for life)
Still the tech bangs for everyone on the main,
Net won't ever again be the same, still
I'm representin' for all the degens all across the world
(Still) Ridin' out the bear like M Cozomo, girl
Still building with the bulls despite the greed
And I still got love for Web3, it's the D.R.E.
https://twitter.com/aSeldomSeenKid/status/1612228771649839105
We don't read poetry because its cute JK
